OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be a
OL,6,Fdry evening with some late brightness.
OL,7,FThe night will then remain largely dry
OL,8,Fwith clear spells. A mild night with
OL,9,Fgentle winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSunday:FA largely dry day with bright
OL,12,Fspells. Cloud will thicken at times in
OL,13,Fthe west to bring the odd spot of rain.
OL,14,
OL,15,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FRather
OL,16,Fcloudy on Monday with a little rain at
OL,17,Ffirst, but otherwise dry with plenty
OL,18,Fof sunshine. Remaining quite warm for
OL,19,Fmost but becoming cooler along the
OL,20,Feast coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
